comments: Vucevic (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Trier (NYK) and allows Trier to maintain his legal guarding position.
RATR and LATR show that Fournier (ORL) places his left hand to Jenkins' (NYK) near arm and then removes it.
Robinson (NYK) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Augustin (ORL) and allows Augustin to maintain his legal guarding position.
LAR shows Mudiay (NYK) briefly extends his right arm into Augustin (ORL) during Augustin's drive to the basket and does not affect his SQBR.
Ellenson (NYK) moves along Gordon's (ORL) path and does not affect his SQBR.
Mudiay (NYK) and Vucevic (ORL) engage during the rebound.
RAR shows Jenkins (NYK) makes marginal hand to hand contact with Vucevic (ORL) as both players attempt to secure the rebound.
Robinson (NYK) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Fournier (ORL) and allows Fournier to maintain his legal guarding position.

LAR shows Fournier (ORL) is drawn into the air as Trier (NYK) pump-fakes prior to his natural upward shooting motion. Fournier maintains his legal guarding position as he reestablishes both feet on the ground prior to Trier's upward shooting motion. Trier leans into Fournier in an unnatural shooting motion in an attempt to draw excessive contact.
On contact between Robinson (NYK) and Vucevic (ORL) during the rebound, Robinson briefly extends his right arm into Vucevic but does not prevent Vucevic from securing the rebound.
Mudiay (NYK) and Vucevic (ORL) engage off ball before Vucevic receives the pass.

LAR shows Mudiay (NYK) briefly puts his hand on Vucevic's (ORL) back, but he doesn't grasp his jersey.  Following the initial contact, Mudiay makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it from Vucevic's possession.
Vucevic (ORL) commits a personal take foul on Mudiay (NYK).

Vucevic (ORL) does not establish himself in Trier's (NYK) path before the contact and extends his arms into Trier as Trier attempts to get around the screen, affecting his ability to contest Ross' (ORL) shot attempt.
Gordon (ORL) commits a personal foul take on Trier (NYK).
Mudiay (NYK) extends his arm in Gordon's (ORL) path and impedes his progress.
Fournier (ORL) and Trier (NYK) engage before the pass.
Thomas (NYK) and Ross (ORL) briefly engage and disengage as Ross attempts to receive the pass from Vucevic (ORL).
Gordon (ORL) commits a personal take foul on Mudiay (NYK).
Ross (ORL) and Trier (NYK) engage and disengage as Ross attempts to receive the pass from Gordon (ORL).
